commit.message: Added Hackage and travis-ci buttons to the README

Add Semigroup s => Semigroup (CI s) instance.

This commit depends on #19 being merged.

Data.Semigroup is part of base as of GHC 8/base-4.9.0.0, semigroups is
added as a conditional dependency for older GHC versions.

Add CHANGELOG to extra-source files so that it shows up on Hackage

Bump version to 1.2.0.3
Renamed NEWS to CHANGELOG so that it shows up on Hackage
bump base and deepseq upper bounds for GHC 7.10 compatibility
Derived a Data instance for CI
